snippet.title: Wendy Williams Is Officially Cancelled After Insulting Dead Teen On LIVE TV
snippet.description:
Wendy Williams Is Officially Cancelled After Insulting Dead Teen On LIVE TV
When it comes to talk show hosts, there are usually a few different types that you can usually count on seeing. There are ones who are meant to be comedy-focused. There are those who want to connect with their audience and make them both feel good about themselves as well as entertaining them in meaningful ways...and then...there are the controversial hosts. The ones who are NEVER afraid to go and open their mouths and say whatever comes to mind. And in this modern generation the best example of that is Wendy Williams. Her big mouth has gotten her in trouble A LOT and it's happened once again in literally the worst way possible. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!
